     48px white arrow chip, #262626 dark cards, purple-tinted light bands.
   • Sections marked  ⟨PLACEHOLDER⟩  need real assets/words from you and are
     styled so they look intentional until you swap them in. Search this file
     for "PLACEHOLDER" to find every spot to edit.
=========================================================================== */

